acceptance_criteria: "One facet grammar covers all 8 annotation surfaces with identical flags and payloads; every old spelling dispatches through the alias shim with a migration hint; spelling-parity spec proves identical output old vs new; contracts, completions (bash/zsh/fish), docs, and MCP names regenerate from the contract table; top-level help lists item facets under a single noun entry."
